name: 2021-04-12 Automatism Figures
description: I painted without much conscious thought in ZenBrush, and it turned out something like rock or folk art figures. Virtual oil and palette knife painting backdrop done in Corel Painter, blended into virtual messy paint and batik via Filter Forge. Composited and adjusted in Photoshop with custom noise alpha on layers. 2732 x 2048 pixels (5.60 MPixels) (4:3) png.
